Class RegisterController

  • java.lang.Object
    • control.RegisterController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScreensIF

    public class RegisterController
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScreensIF
    This class manage the actions when the guest forward to registration. some of the functions here listen to actions in the menu and some include some algorithms for registration.
